oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Nashville Cats - the Jordanaires - October 25, 2008
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Program on the life and career of the vocal group the Jordanaires. Recorded in the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on October 25, 2008.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Jordanaires;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Interview program hosted by Bill Lloyd. Interview with group members Gordon Stoker and Ray Walker. Includes selected excerpts from recordings, audio from video.
